231
00:15:26,140 --> 00:15:26,980
My Lord,

232
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:29,100
I'll go.

233
00:15:29,950 --> 00:15:30,790
Good.

234
00:15:31,260 --> 00:15:33,660
Zhan Bie, come back soon.

235
00:15:33,860 --> 00:15:34,700
I will.

236
00:15:42,310 --> 00:15:43,150
My Lord,

237
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:45,500
