704
00:40:52,032 --> 00:40:58,152
♪The soul fire burns me all the time♪

705
00:40:58,562 --> 00:41:04,042
♪Asking me what I want♪

706
00:41:04,552 --> 00:41:06,642
♪What I actually want♪

707
00:41:06,642 --> 00:41:12,632
♪Give me God's wings
